Car Craft - June 2014  USA

108 Pages | True PDF | English | 23 MB 


Car Craft is the musclecar enthusiasts magazine. This magazine focuses on post-1949 high-performance cars and specializes in '60s and '70s musclecars. Each issue is filled with how-to guides on car restoration, engine rebuilding and tuning, product reviews and performance tests, car show coverage and event schedules. Car Craft is for serious musclecar enthusiasts.
